sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant K as Kafka
    participant R as Redis

    Note over U,R: 0. Authentication
    U->>KC: POST /login {username, password}
    KC-->>U: accessToken + refreshToken

    Note over U,R: 1. Join Stream
    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/join {userId}
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>K: publish ViewerJoined {streamId, userId}
        V-->>U: 200 OK
        K->>V: consume ViewerJoined
        V->>R: SADD viewers {userId}
        R-->>V: 1 (new) or 0 (duplicate)
        alt new viewer
            V->>R: INCR viewer_count
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        else duplicate
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        end
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over U,R: 2. Leave Stream
    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/leave {userId}
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>K: publish ViewerLeft {streamId, userId}
        V-->>U: 200 OK
        K->>V: consume ViewerLeft
        V->>R: SREM viewers {userId}
        R-->>V: 1 (removed) or 0 (not found)
        alt removed
            V->>R: DECR viewer_count
            V->>R: DEL viewer:{userId}
        else not found
            Note over V: Ignore
        end
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over U,R: 3. Get Viewer Count
    U->>V: GET /streams/{streamId}/viewers
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>R: GET viewer_count
        R-->>V: N
        V-->>U: 200 OK {viewerCount: N}
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end